*pambase-20080221 (21 Feb 2008)

  21 Feb 2008; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -pambase-20080219.1.ebuild, +pambase-20080221.ebuild:
  Bump pambase, now it supports gnome and consolekit USE flags that allows it
